"title": "8135: knowing God, nature of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8135",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>To know God is not merely to know things about him, such as his character, but also to experience his presence and power. To know God is to be transformed by him. Human knowledge of God is as a result of God's revelation of himself.</p>\n<h2>The origin of knowing God</h2>\n<h3>Knowing God depends on revelation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:33-Rom11:36\">ROM 11:33–11:36</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:13\">ISA 40:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:29\">DEU 29:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:6\">NUM 12:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num23:3\">NUM 23:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job12:22\">JOB 12:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:5\">ISA 40:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:1\">ISA 65:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:5\">EZK 20:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:20-Dan2:23\">DAN 2:20–2:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:28\">DAN 2:28</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos4:13\">AMO 4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:25-Matt11:27\">MAT 11:25–11:27</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:21-Luke10:22\">LUK 10:21–10:22</a> <em>Jesus Christ praises the Father for the revelation the disciples receive</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:25-Rom16:26\">ROM 16:25–16:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:12\">GAL 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:4-Eph3:5\">EPH 3:4–3:5</a></p>\n<h3>God gives knowledge of his reality through creation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:20\">ROM 1:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps8:1\">PSA 8:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:1-Ps19:4\">PSA 19:1–19:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:6\">PSA 97:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:17\">ACT 14:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:24-Acts17:27\">ACT 17:24–17:27</a></p>\n<h3>God gives knowledge of his mercy and his will through Scripture, both law and gospel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:17\">ROM 1:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:13\">DEU 31:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:36\">ACT 10:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:20-1Cor1:21\">1CO 1:20–1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb8:10-Heb8:11\">HEB 8:10–8:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:33-Jer31:34\">JER 31:33–31:34</a></p>\n<h3>God gives knowledge of himself through Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:27\">MAT 11:27</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:22\">LUK 10:22</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:2\">JHN 3:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:19\">JHN 8:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:32\">JHN 10:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:7\">JHN 14:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:30\">JHN 16:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:3\">JHN 17:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:2\">COL 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:9-2Tim1:10\">2TI 1:9–1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:20-1Pet1:21\">1PE 1:20–1:21</a></p>\n<h3>God gives knowledge of himself and his ways through the Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:17\">EPH 1:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:2\">ISA 11:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:16-John14:17\">JHN 14:16–14:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:26\">JHN 14:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:26\">JHN 15:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:12-John16:15\">JHN 16:12–16:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:31\">ACT 4:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:9-1Cor2:11\">1CO 2:9–2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:8\">1CO 12:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:16-Eph3:19\">EPH 3:16–3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:12\">1PE 1:12</a></p>\n<h3>God gives knowledge of his greatness and grace through experience of him, submission to him and in answer to prayer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps56:9-Ps56:11\">PSA 56:9–56:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:29\">EXO 9:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps17:6-Ps17:7\">PSA 17:6–17:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:19-Ps66:20\">PSA 66:19–66:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:19-Isa41:20\">ISA 41:19–41:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:3-Isa45:6\">ISA 45:3–45:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa50:4\">ISA 50:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:16\">ISA 60:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:16\">JER 22:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer24:7\">JER 24:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek6:7\">EZK 6:7</a></p>\n<h2>The nature of knowing God</h2>\n<h3>Knowing his character</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:2\">JON 4:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:9\">DEU 7:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:10\">PSA 9:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps36:10\">PSA 36:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps135:5\">PSA 135:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:3-1Thess4:5\">1TH 4:3–4:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:8\">1JN 4:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:16\">1JN 4:16</a></p>\n<h3>Knowing his words and works</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos3:7\">AMO 3:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:25\">GEN 41:25</a> <em>Pharaoh</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod6:6-Exod6:7\">EXO 6:6–6:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:5\">EXO 7:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:17\">EXO 7:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod18:11\">EXO 18:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:291\">DEU 29:291</a>SA <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut3:7\">3:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam3:211\">1SA 3:211</a>SA <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:46\">17:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:21\">2SA 7:21</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr17:19\">1CH 17:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:27\">2SA 7:27</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr17:25\">1CH 17:25</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs8:10\">2KI 8:10</a> <em>Elisha</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:19\">2KI 19:19</a> <em>Hezekiah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:19\">PSA 147:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:9\">EZK 20:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:26\">LUK 2:26</a> <em>Simeon</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:8\">JHN 17:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:22\">ACT 2:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:14\">ACT 22:14</a></p>\n<h3>To know Jesus Christ is to know God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:6\">JHN 14:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:15\">COL 1:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:16-Matt16:17\">MAT 16:16–16:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:19\">JHN 8:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:15\">JHN 15:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:15\">JHN 16:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:26\">JHN 17:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:2-Col2:3\">COL 2:2–2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:20\">1JN 5:20</a></p>\n<h3>To know God is to experience his salvation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:3\">JHN 17:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps17:6-Ps17:7\">PSA 17:6–17:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:9\">ISA 25:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:12\">ISA 43:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:10\">ISA 52:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:1\">ISA 56:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:13\">1JN 5:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:20\">1JN 5:20</a></p>",
